      "created_at": "2017-06-16T17:53:03.860Z",
      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/f/ff41900a58f8980003c4655c748eddf8ee0a97a3.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/ff41900a58f8980003c4655c748eddf8ee0a97a3\" title=\"trump.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/ff41900a58f8980003c4655c748eddf8ee0a97a3_2_800x576.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/ff41900a58f8980003c4655c748eddf8ee0a97a3_2_800x576.jpg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/ff41900a58f8980003c4655c748eddf8ee0a97a3_2_1200x864.jpg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/ff41900a58f8980003c4655c748eddf8ee0a97a3_2_1600x1152.jpg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/ff41900a58f8980003c4655c748eddf8ee0a97a3_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">trump.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">4195×3022 1.18 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>“Po hetohem për pushimin nga puna të drejtorit të FBI-së nga njeriu që më tha ta pushoja drejtorin nga puna! Gjueti shtrigash” - ka qënë mesazhi i parë që Presidenti Trump ka lëshuar sot në Twitter, duke konfirmuar në një farë mënyre ato që spekulloheshin në mediat. Sipas CNN, që citon burime brenda WH, njeriu në fjalë është Rod Rosenstein, zv Drejtori i Departamentit të drejtësisë. Rodenstein kishte shkruar një memo ku kritikonte punën e James Comeyt në krye të FBI-së. Fillimisht shkarkimi i Comeyt nga Trump u justifikua si e bazuar mbi rekomandimet e Rosenstein por më pas Trump pohoi se e kishte pushuar Comeyn në lidhje me “punën e Rusisë”. Ndërkohë, po në Twitter Presidenti sot u shpreh entuziast me mbështetjen publike që gëzon, 50%, sipas një sondazhi.</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox twitterstatus\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/875701471999864833?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump-james-comey-investigated%2Findex.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">twitter.com</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/874276197357596672/kUuht00m_400x400.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail onebox-avatar\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\">\n<h4>\n  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/875701471999864833?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump-james-comey-investigated%2Findex.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">\n    Donald J. Trump (realDonaldTrump)\n  </a>\n</h4>\n\n<div class=\"tweet\">I am being investigated for firing the FBI Director by the man who told me to fire the FBI Director! Witch Hunt</div>\n\n<div class=\"date\">\n  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/875701471999864833?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump-james-comey-investigated%2Findex.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">1:07 PM - 16 Jun 2017</a>\n    <span class=\"like\">\n      <svg viewbox=\"0 0 512 512\" width=\"14px\" height=\"16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <path d=\"M462.3 62.6C407.5 15.9 326 24.3 275.7 76.2L256 96.5l-19.7-20.3C186.1 24.3 104.5 15.9 49.7 62.6c-62.8 53.6-66.1 149.8-9.9 207.9l193.5 199.8c12.5 12.9 32.8 12.9 45.3 0l193.5-199.8c56.3-58.1 53-154.3-9.8-207.9z\"></path>\n      </svg> 140K\n    </span>\n    <span class=\"retweet\">\n      <svg viewbox=\"0 0 640 512\" width=\"14px\" height=\"16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <path d=\"M629.657 343.598L528.971 444.284c-9.373 9.372-24.56